Day 12 - Manga 272* 
Some shitty works together that have no connection with each other. Like my friend down there said, I like the part where the girl uses another version of herself(?) to masturbate. But my friend really liked it huh? 1/10.
Also, yeah, unfortunately, I'm still alive. Don't know for how much more time but still here.
Also also, if you know how to add someone on smite, send me an friend invite, the name is SoutaMarufugi, I sometimes play the game and we might be able to play together. If you need anything else, click my profile, go to my recent comments open the one in which I stopped and write a message, I'll probably see it.
This is an insult to my eyes 2/10
never fucking mind then, but uhh what the fuck? 3/10

One of the best Eva-Doujin. The Part with Asuka is hot but the one with Rei an inferno. Few times I have seen an artist addressing Reis otherworldly state of mind in such drastic pictures. To be completely precise Rei isn't using those limbs for masturbation, she is just using herself. The presentation of fisting and the corresponding facial expressions are also first rate and disturbingly realistic. A secret masterpiece of artwork.
